Commentary Text: U Yadav to Maxwell, out Caught by Uthappa!! Mad max Maxi is gone. This is a body blow for Punjab. Two wickets in two overs and the pendulum swings back in favour of KKR now. It was a pacy back of a length delivery, Maxwell backed away towards the leg-side, perhaps was undone by the bounce there. He is tucked up for room, ends up having a slash at it.
